    <!-- Where each array can be found with R.array.<name>
    index 0 will be the monster stage
    index 1 will be the number monster evolutions
    index 2 will be the description title
    index 3 will be the description
    index 4 will be the monster icon
    index 5 - (5+number of evolutions-1) is the different possible evolutions
    index (5+number of evolutions) is the standard health of the monster
    index (5+number of evolutions+1) is the standard attack power of the monster
    index (5+number of evolutions+2) is the standard attack chance of the monster
    index (5+number of evolutions+3) is the evolution diligence requirement of the monster
    index (5+number of evolutions+4) is the hunger requirement
    index (5+number of evolutions+5) is the max overfeed/gluttony
    index (5+number of evolutions+6) is the max training mistakes-->

